[test robust.it]
# gen130 (L20-deep), Italian probe: the SAME self-perturbation sweep reached
# through the Italian trigger ("da cosa dipende …"). One mechanism, two
# languages, one code path — the bilingual ratchet.

> socrate è un uomo
< Learned: man(socrate).
> ogni uomo è un mortale
< Learned rule: mortal(X) :- man(X).
> socrate è un mortale?
< Yes.
> da cosa dipende questa conclusione?
< My conclusion that socrate is a mortal is fragile: it rests entirely on one fact — man(socrate). Forget that and it falls.

